item.title: [HIVE-20433] Implicit String to Timestamp conversion is slow
item.description:
getTimestampFromString() is slow at casting dates. It throws twice before date conversion can happen.

 

cc gopalv ashutoshc
item.summary: Implicit String to Timestamp conversion is slow

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.
